Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:01.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:03.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:05.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings\na group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:08.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled by{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:11.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the few remaining shards of the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:13.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:14.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:17.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to a genealogy scroll\nfound at Hojo's house,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:20.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}his ancestor, Akitoki Hojo,\nhad a wife{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.09,0:00:21.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}whose name was Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:24.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Could that mean me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sacred Jewel which is said\nto grant one's every wish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to search for the shards\nof the shattered Sacred Jewel,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:10.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I began crossing between\nthe present and the feudal age{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:13.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the hidden well\nin my family's shrine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:18.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But at times, I return to\nthe present world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}to attend classes like any normal\njunior high-school student,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}studying and doing my best\nin tests.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}None of my school friends\nknows about my other life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:33.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I really don't think anyone\nwould believe me anyway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:41.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:43.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't get it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:45.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't understand it at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, time's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:53.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:58.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was confident about history...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Especially since it's on the feudal age.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a shock!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:09.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been absent a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I probably have to\ntake a make-up test.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want me to take it\nwith you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:20.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're in school today!\NAre you feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:23.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:26.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I found something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a scroll of the\NHojo family tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:31.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By my ancestor, Akitoki Hojo,\nwho lived 500 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,during the feudal {\i1}age....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:38.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at his wife's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?!\N- Is it for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:42.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It says, "Kagome"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- No...!\N- No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:51.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's right! That's my name\non the Hojo family tree...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a shock, that among\nthe Hojo ancestors
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:04.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is someone named Kagome Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Kagome breaks up with that\ndelinquent boyfriend of hers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:11.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and hooks up with Hojo,\nher name'll be Kagome Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe that's not just a\ngenealogy chart,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but a prophecy scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:17.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo might be thinking\njust that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you think, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:22.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd better brush up\non history again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome isn't in the mood\nto talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:29.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh {\i1}yes....{\i0} I developed the pictures\NI took at the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:31.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:32.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow, nice pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say!\NKagome looks so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:39.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real demon is also\nin the picture!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:46.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey {\i1}mister....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:49.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave all your belongings\nand go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:50.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Defy us and you'll get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give us all your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:57.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,People will dislike you if\nyou're too bossy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:01.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You men speak as though\nyou're robbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's exactly what we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop acting so dense and\nhand over the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:09.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Caught in a bind again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're looking well, Akitoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo and Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming\nto my rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:25.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:27.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:29.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pickled plums?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm told they're good for you.\NTry one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By the way, what're you\ndoing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:38.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's a long {\i1}story....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:41.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I need to ask something\nof the priestess, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Old Kaede?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You wanna ask her something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:51.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0} You're on a mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:52.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is something called Kenkon,\nthe Naginata of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This naginata is a demonic weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:01.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which has a blade affixed to\neither end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:02.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demonic weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Recently, the Hojo family has\nbeen plagued with misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:09.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the source of the misfortune\nis supposedly the blade
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:12.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,of this Naginata of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:14.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? This {\i1}is....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:16.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demonic aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It looks so ominous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:19.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:23.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Put it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:25.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:27.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh! Snap out of it, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:32.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:34.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were about to be possessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:37.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We were told that an exorcism\nwould be necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in order to disperse\nthe demonic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:41.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But as you just saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the power of the blade\nis too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:47.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it was decided to purify it\nat Mt. Hakurei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I was chosen\nto fulfill the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But that {\i1}mountain....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:54.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:58.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just recently, a natural disaster\ncaused the mountain to totally collapse
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,leaving not even a trace\nof its former glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If the blade cannot be purified,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:09.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Hojo family will continue\nto be plagued with ill fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:15.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so, you came to me in search\nof another solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:20.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone suggested that I seek\nyou out for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's that peak over yonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:31.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Deep in that mountain is\nthe sacred Shrine of Furai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you were to entrust\nthe blade to that {\i1}shrine....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:36.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the demonic aura should\ndissipate by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:37.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Shrine of Furai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Around here, it is the holiest place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:44.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But just what is\N"deep in the mountain"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A river flows to the east of the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:54.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you follow it upriver,\nyou will come upon Shoun Falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Furai Shrine is apparently\nclose to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shoun Falls?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:02.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please everyone, accompany me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NWhat'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was accosted by robbers earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but ever since I've had possession\nof that blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,bad things continually happen\nto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Akitoki is my vassal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:20.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a master's responsibility to\ncome to the aid of his servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:24.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome will be returning\nhere soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Kagome will come, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis, are you sure\nyou have everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:38.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm taking my textbooks this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I'll be able to study\nover there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:41.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm all ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe this time, I'll say you\nhit your head
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and suffered amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandpa, amnesia is\na bit {\i1}extreme....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:51.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Buyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know! How about cat allergy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or you became paralyzed from\na voodoo doll that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,was sent to us for\npurification.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:00.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, here's your bento lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:04.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You made so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:08.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can share it with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:13.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:17.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, which one will it be?\NCat allergy or the voodoo doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish she was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:41.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:47.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're Hojo's ancestor, Akitoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:52.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here! The ninja food I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Vietnamese {\i1}flavor....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I found some new products.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:02.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:03.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's sulking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:04.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:06.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He doesn't like the idea of\nhelping Akitoki and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:09.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,delaying the search for\nthe Sacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:17.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:20.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sulking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is sulking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard the story from Old Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:32.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo is in trouble.\NWe should help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what about\nthe Sacred Jewel shards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What if Naraku gets\nthem first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand that, {\i1}but....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:42.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because Mt. Hakurei\ndisintegrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo can't carry out his mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you feel sorry for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Naraku's fault that\nthe mountain collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you can't just ignore\nsomeone in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:56.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're too nice to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:00.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is such a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:01.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:09.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since Kagome asked, I'll take\nyou to the waterfall or shrine or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:13.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So get your business over with quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's such a hardhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:28.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I shall enjoy\nyour mother's cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:32.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:38.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's try going to\nthe foot of the mountain first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:43.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It transformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, get on her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about Kagome and\nyou others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll ride on Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:53.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku is pretty fast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:55.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit dawdling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:01.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-They're so {\i1}fast....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, let's get going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:07.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:12.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:14.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:22.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome's smile\nis so cute...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hojo's ancestor, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:30.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The name, Kagome,\nthat was listed on{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the family tree scroll\nthat Hojo showed me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What if...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't return to\nthe modern age and{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}ended up marrying\NHojo here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:47.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Look, Miroku,\na river!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:51.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That must be the river that\nflows east of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:57.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey {\i1}Akitoki....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why didn't you think about\ngetting rid of that blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:04.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then another family besides\nours would suffer misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:08.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must have the blade purified.\NThat's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:13.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo, you're quite manly,\naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:19.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And this {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The guy's a wimp. He should\nstop acting so brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- That wasn't necessary, Inuyasha.\N- Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err....{\i0} Yes, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:32.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're finally coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:47.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A teahouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, there's a teahouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank goodness for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:55.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ohh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:00.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! My sandals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Both the {\i1}thongs....!{\i0}\NThis bodes {\i1}ill....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This blade brings so\nmuch bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aww man! Take a break?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why humans are\nsuch a pain to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:20.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, don't judge us against\nyour brute strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're made of delicate flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:25.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These dumplings are delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:28.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:36.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:38.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:43.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There goes Kagome\nwith her ninja bag of tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a cold compress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just the thing to\ncool your burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:57.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yes! It's starting to\nfeel cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:00.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:03.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! A lunch box of goodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This omelet is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The simmered vegetables\nare great, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:15.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I prefer the ninja food\nyou add hot water to-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then, I shall {\i1}try....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:21.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait! My rice ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:27.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:32.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This blade brings\nsuch bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:43.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just having it in your possession\nbrings misfortune, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:45.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You saw what happened\njust now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:49.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, a lot of little mishaps\nhave been happening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you making too\nmuch of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:57.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, this blade brings misfortune\nto whoever possesses it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:59.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A succession of small mishaps, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess if they happen one\nafter another, it's hard to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:12.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That blade is a demonic blade.\NHumans shouldn't possess it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:15.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He should just get\nrid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:17.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo is doing his best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though he's weak and\ngets airsick, he's doing his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:26.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Makes you want to help\nand encourage him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why're you defending him\nso much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:29.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:33.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon blades can only be\nhandled by demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,or half-demons like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:37.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's impossible for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:38.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:43.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans shouldn't get involved!\NYou guys just don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Hey Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:16:59.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:03.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Health before a mission.\NEat, Akitoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I accept {\i1}with....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:09.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:26.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're coming right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:33.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Leave 'em to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who could have done that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:48.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I smell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:52.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The smell of explosives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Explosives?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look! Up in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was that a bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It looked like a kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never seen a strange\nkite like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:10.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:17.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:25.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:28.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A sacred arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:36.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He pulled up those huge {\i1}boulders....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:45.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who was he anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:54.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku....{\i0} Do you think\nhe was after the blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:58.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,During that last attack,\nhe targeted Akitoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:18:59.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I'd guess, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:03.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The blade brings {\i1}misfortune....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:05.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that's why I keep\ntelling {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just let 'em have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:10.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If the enemy wants this blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,then he must already\nhave the Kon blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Kon blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:19.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Naginata of Heaven and Earth,\nor Kenkon, was so frighteningly powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:25.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that the blade was divided\ninto two blades, the Ken and Kon blades,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:30.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and sent away - one to the north\nand one to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:35.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And one of the blades was\nentrusted to the Hojo family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what if the two blades\nare joined?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:43.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Specific details weren't\npassed down to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:46.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Crows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:49.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:56.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How I've missed you,\NMaster Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:00.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's up, Myoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Err.... Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that Mt. Hakurei\nhas disintegrated, Totosai {\i1}said....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:11.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That holy mountain kept\nmany things sealed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:16.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I fear that the Naginata of\NKenkon which was left by Kaijinbo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}will appear again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:21.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he was quite worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:22.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:24.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Naginata of {\i1}Kenkon....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:26.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was forged by the demon\NKaijinbo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:32.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Master Inuyasha, if it's possible,\NTotosai wants you to seal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I came in\nsearch of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:37.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:40.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only he can do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that's what he said to\ntell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:44.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not "hah", Master Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:52.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one after the blade is\nthe leader of the demon ninjas, Hoshiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:54.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon ninjas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:55.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:58.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon ninjas are just that -\ndemons versed in the ninja ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:04.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Hoshiyomi is the one who\nmade Kaijinbo forge the Naginata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sacred arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:08.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:23.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll reach Furai Shrine\ntomorrow, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:24.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:26.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:31.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seems they haven't learned\ntheir lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They must be after\nthe Ken blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo! This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:39.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:41.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:42.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:45.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:48.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:53.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Akitoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.79,0:22:04.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.76,0:23:47.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're Hoshiyomi, the one\nafter the Ken blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.83,0:23:49.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you want it so badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.80,0:23:52.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This doesn't concern you,\nso there's no need to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:55.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fearsome Demon Ninjas\nattack our group...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:58.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and Akitoki and I become\nseparated from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.78,0:24:02.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never imagined that just the two of us\nwould head towards Furai Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.01,0:24:04.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh? Just the two of us?! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:09.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Mountain of Demons: Survival of the Duo"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now can this be called\na fortunate misfortune?
